> Almost every modern Flutter app — *Swiggy, Zomato, WhatsApp, IRCTC, Google Pay* — relies on this triad. The `http` package (official Dart team) handles **HTTP**, the `dart:convert` library handles **JSON**, and the architectural philosophy of REST governs **API design**. Mastering these three is *non-negotiable* for any mobile developer.

