## 3.2 Analytical Matrix — What Each Layer Solves

| Problem | Solved By | Specific Construct in This Project |
|---|---|---|
| UI doesn't reflect DB changes | Reactive state | `ChangeNotifier` + `notifyListeners()` + `context.watch` |
| State lost on hot reload | Stateful widget for form fields | `_NoteEditorScreenState` with `TextEditingController` |
| Data lost on app kill | Persistent storage | `sqflite` `notes` table on disk |
| DB connection leaks | Singleton | `DatabaseHelper.instance` |
| UI tightly coupled to DB | Repository pattern | `NoteRepository` |
| Memory leaks from controllers | Proper dispose | `_title.dispose()` + `_body.dispose()` |
| Hard to test logic | Pure view-model | `NotesViewModel` (no `BuildContext` dependency) |

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **KTU Project Evaluation:** Your project will be marked on the presence of *this exact separation of concerns*. Mixing SQL queries inside `build()` methods is an automatic 4-mark penalty.

