> **KTU Examiner's Valuation Warning — Common Pitfalls:**
>
> 1. **Forgetting `notifyListeners()`** — Your UI never updates. (-2 marks)
> 2. **Storing JWT in plain text SharedPreferences** — Use `flutter_secure_storage` instead. (-2 marks)
> 3. **Using `print()` for debugging in production code** — Use proper logging libraries. (-1 mark)
> 4. **Not handling `DioException` separately from generic `Exception`** — Loses 1–2 marks on error handling.
> 5. **Hardcoding API base URLs in multiple files** — Should be in a single `config.dart`. (-1 mark)
> 6. **Forgetting `WidgetsFlutterBinding.ensureInitialized()` before `Firebase.initializeApp()`** — Causes runtime crash. (-2 marks)
> 7. **Not using `FieldValue.serverTimestamp()` in Firestore** — Client clocks may be wrong, breaking message ordering. (-1 mark)
